    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>&quot;Tech Store Simulator&quot;</strong> is an engaging first-person simulation where every aspect of running an electronic shop comes to life. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Design your store</strong>, optimizing for both efficiency and aesthetics. Determine the best display for your tech gadgets, manage your aisles, and ensure a seamless shopping experience for your customers. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3076400/extras/ab474119c6b3c1348b69c75662197d65.poster.avif?t=1738220533\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3076400/extras/ab474119c6b3c1348b69c75662197d65.webm?t=1738220533\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3076400/extras/ab474119c6b3c1348b69c75662197d65.mp4?t=1738220533\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>Order stock using an in-game computer</strong>. Unpack the latest tech gadgets, organize them in your storage room, and strategically place them on shelves and displays.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3076400/extras/5f3f87d9fe2fe3c2898ee32ae8eb2cb2.poster.avif?t=1738220533\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3076400/extras/5f3f87d9fe2fe3c2898ee32ae8eb2cb2.webm?t=1738220533\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3076400/extras/5f3f87d9fe2fe3c2898ee32ae8eb2cb2.mp4?t=1738220533\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>Handle customer</strong> transactions by scanning items and making sure customers leave satisfied with their shopping and checkout experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3076400/extras/7b09e74c934bf170e0e36686ad7bc25e.poster.avif?t=1738220533\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3076400/extras/7b09e74c934bf170e0e36686ad7bc25e.webm?t=1738220533\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3076400/extras/7b09e74c934bf170e0e36686ad7bc25e.mp4?t=1738220533\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>Be careful of thieves.</strong> Not all clients want you to make money. Some of them just want to pick up and run. In this case, only a magic kick will help!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3076400/extras/2586684e305017854a4d81be142b75bc.poster.avif?t=1738220533\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3076400/extras/2586684e305017854a4d81be142b75bc.webm?t=1738220533\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3076400/extras/2586684e305017854a4d81be142b75bc.mp4?t=1738220533\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Customers come in many forms.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Some clients will be nice to you, some not so nice, but you should be able to capitalize on all situations!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3076400/extras/48b62e3c962bfb2d74fab11819cee619.poster.avif?t=1738220533\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3076400/extras/48b62e3c962bfb2d74fab11819cee619.webm?t=1738220533\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3076400/extras/48b62e3c962bfb2d74fab11819cee619.mp4?t=1738220533\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>In &quot;Tech Store Simulator&quot;, every decision matters.</strong> Will you rise to the occasion, transforming a modest tech store into a retail powerhouse, while balancing customer satisfaction and finances?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
